bi bana sakta ha name sa kisi bi name ka data type bana sakta han neacha example bi de hoye ha apko or han structure ka use user defined data type ka lia hota ha
Data type 2 tarha ke hoti han Build in data type or user defined data type ::
Example::>

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
struct Masroor
{
    float number;
    float total;
};
int main(){
Masroor m;
cout<<"Enter the total marks ::> ";
cin>>m.total;
cout<<"Enter the Obtained number :: >> ";
cin>>m.number;

cout<<"The percantage of the number is ::> "<<m.number*100/m.total<<endl;
return 0; 
}



